%% Diagram: Modern rendering strategy decision tree
%% Type: flowchart
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
flowchart TD
    Start{"What is the page?"}
    Start -->|Marketing / docs<br/>content-heavy| Q1{"Any interactivity?"}
    Start -->|Catalog / product<br/>large + SEO| Q2{"Updates per minute?"}
    Start -->|Personalized<br/>per-request data| Q3{"Public shell + private data?"}
    Start -->|App / dashboard<br/>auth-gated| Q4{"SEO matters?"}

    Q1 -->|None| A1["SSG<br/>(zero JS)"]
    Q1 -->|A few widgets| A2["SSG + Islands<br/>(Astro / Fresh)"]

    Q2 -->|Few| A3["ISR + on-demand<br/>revalidation"]
    Q2 -->|Many| A4["SSR + CDN cache<br/>+ short TTL"]

    Q3 -->|Yes| A5["PPR / RSC<br/>(static shell + streamed dynamic)"]
    Q3 -->|All dynamic| A6["SSR + Suspense<br/>streaming"]

    Q4 -->|No| A7["CSR (SPA)<br/>or RSC + use client"]
    Q4 -->|Yes| A6
